window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Born in fire. Tempered in blood.</b></p> <p>Epheria is a land divided by war and mistrust. The High Lords of the South squabble and fight, only kept in check by the Dragonguard, traitors of a time long past, who serve the empire of the North.</p> <p>In the remote villages of Southern Epheria, still reeling from the tragic loss of his brother, Calen Bryer prepares for The Proving - a test of courage and skill that not all survive. But when three strangers arrive in the village of Milltown, with a secret they are willing to die for, Calen’s world is ripped from under him and he is thrust headfirst into a war that has been raging for centuries.</p> <p>There is no prophecy. His coming was not foretold. He bleeds like any man, and bleed he will.</p> <p>Includes bonus story <i>The Fall</i>.</p>"; 
